        Constructs a MovementManner instance, describing the manner in which the robot should complete a given RobotMovement path.

        marginOfError - A double describing how far the robot can be from its endpoint in order for the path to be considered finished, in inches.
        speedSupplier - A MovementManner.MovementSpeedSupplier which provides the speed the robot should move at given the total distance of the path and the remaining distance to travel.
